    • Constructor Detail

      • Day

        public Day(int day,
           int month,
           int year)
        Constructor that sets the data of the day. If the day is not valid the day will be initialized to 0. If the month is not valid the month will be initialized to 0.
        Parameters:
        day - int - The day of the month. Depending on the month this can be a range from 0-28 to 0-31
        month - int - The month of the year. January is month 0, December is month 12
        year - int - The year
        Since:
        1.0
